metadata.name: Api::V1::Accounts::StatusesController GET #index with someone else's pinned statuses when user does not follow account lists the public status only

sql_query.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM "oauth_access_tokens" WHERE "oauth_access_tokens"."token" = $1 LIMIT $2
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "oauth_access_tokens" WHERE "oauth_access_tokens"."token" = $1 AND "oauth_access_tokens"."id" != $2 LIMIT $3
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "blocks" WHERE "blocks"."account_id" = $1 AND "blocks"."target_account_id" = $2 LIMIT $3
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "follows" WHERE "follows"."account_id" = $1 AND "follows"."target_account_id" = $2 LIMIT $3

SELECT "statuses"."id", "statuses"."updated_at" FROM "statuses" INNER JOIN "status_pins" ON "statuses"."id" = "status_pins"."status_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "mentions" ON "mentions"."status_id" = "statuses"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "statuses" "reblog" ON "reblog"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "reblog"."id" = "statuses"."reblog_of_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "accounts" ON "accounts"."id" = "reblog"."account_id" WHERE "statuses"."account_id" = $1 AND ("statuses"."visibility" IN ($2, $3) OR "mentions"."account_id" = $4) AND ("statuses"."reblog_of_id" IS NULL OR ("accounts"."domain" IS NULL OR 1=1) AND 1=1) AND "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status_pins"."account_id" = $5 GROUP BY "statuses"."id", "status_pins"."created_at" ORDER BY status_pins.created_at DESC, "statuses"."id" DESC LIMIT $6
SELECT "statuses".* FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses"."id" = $1 ORDER BY "statuses"."id" DESC
SELECT "media_attachments".* FROM "media_attachments" WHERE "media_attachments"."status_id" = $1 ORDER BY "media_attachments"."id" ASC
